<Link id="l00114" /><CodeLine lineNumber="114"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">  /// This enumeration defines the supported behaviors of module flags.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00115" /><CodeLine lineNumber="115" lineLink="/docs/api/classes/llvm/module/#a0a5c55e12c97b80021330fe82b642293"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">enum</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/module/#a0a5c55e12c97b80021330fe82b642293">ModFlagBehavior</a> &#123;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00116" /><CodeLine lineNumber="116"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">    /// Emits an error if two values disagree, otherwise the resulting value is</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00117" /><CodeLine lineNumber="117"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">    /// that of the operands.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00118" /><CodeLine lineNumber="118" lineLink="/docs/api/classes/llvm/module/#a0a5c55e12c97b80021330fe82b642293a4771bacd44b97e736b819b5d06b22dfe"><span class="doxyHighlight">    <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/module/#a0a5c55e12c97b80021330fe82b642293a4771bacd44b97e736b819b5d06b22dfe">Error</a> = 1,</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00119" /><CodeLine lineNumber="119"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00120" /><CodeLine lineNumber="120"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">    /// Emits a warning if two values disagree. The result value will be the</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00121" /><CodeLine lineNumber="121"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">    /// operand for the flag from the first module being linked.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00122" /><CodeLine lineNumber="122" lineLink="/docs/api/classes/llvm/module/#a0a5c55e12c97b80021330fe82b642293a355bc901e05417401ee44323a8595131"><span class="doxyHighlight">    <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/module/#a0a5c55e12c97b80021330fe82b642293a355bc901e05417401ee44323a8595131">Warning</a> = 2,</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00123" /><CodeLine lineNumber="123"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00124" /><CodeLine lineNumber="124"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">    /// Adds a requirement that another module flag be present and have a</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00125" /><CodeLine lineNumber="125"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">    /// specified value after linking is performed. The value must be a metadata</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00126" /><CodeLine lineNumber="126"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">    /// pair, where the first element of the pair is the ID of the module flag</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00127" /><CodeLine lineNumber="127"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">    /// to be restricted, and the second element of the pair is the value the</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00128" /><CodeLine lineNumber="128"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">    /// module flag should be restricted to. This behavior can be used to</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00129" /><CodeLine lineNumber="129"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">    /// restrict the allowable results (via triggering of an error) of linking</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00130" /><CodeLine lineNumber="130"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">    /// IDs with the &#42;&#42;Override&#42;&#42; behavior.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00131" /><CodeLine lineNumber="131" lineLink="/docs/api/classes/llvm/module/#a0a5c55e12c97b80021330fe82b642293aec0586c2f89c73dcc00841aa000141bb"><span class="doxyHighlight">    <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/module/#a0a5c55e12c97b80021330fe82b642293aec0586c2f89c73dcc00841aa000141bb">Require</a> = 3,</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00132" /><CodeLine lineNumber="132"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00133" /><CodeLine lineNumber="133"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">    /// Uses the specified value, regardless of the behavior or value of the</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00134" /><CodeLine lineNumber="134"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">    /// other module. If both modules specify &#42;&#42;Override&#42;&#42;, but the values</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00135" /><CodeLine lineNumber="135"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">    /// differ, an error will be emitted.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00136" /><CodeLine lineNumber="136" lineLink="/docs/api/classes/llvm/module/#a0a5c55e12c97b80021330fe82b642293a2aba8031539d1446aff14d13c7deea69"><span class="doxyHighlight">    <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/module/#a0a5c55e12c97b80021330fe82b642293a2aba8031539d1446aff14d13c7deea69">Override</a> = 4,</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00137" /><CodeLine lineNumber="137"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00138" /><CodeLine lineNumber="138"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">    /// Appends the two values, which are required to be metadata nodes.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00139" /><CodeLine lineNumber="139" lineLink="/docs/api/classes/llvm/module/#a0a5c55e12c97b80021330fe82b642293a7a6b9b7ed3797ab927caf581353e935a"><span class="doxyHighlight">    <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/module/#a0a5c55e12c97b80021330fe82b642293a7a6b9b7ed3797ab927caf581353e935a">Append</a> = 5,</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00140" /><CodeLine lineNumber="140"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00141" /><CodeLine lineNumber="141"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">    /// Appends the two values, which are required to be metadata</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00142" /><CodeLine lineNumber="142"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">    /// nodes. However, duplicate entries in the second list are dropped</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00143" /><CodeLine lineNumber="143"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">    /// during the append operation.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00144" /><CodeLine lineNumber="144" lineLink="/docs/api/classes/llvm/module/#a0a5c55e12c97b80021330fe82b642293a2486ec4ce4f33e42da3ad60d6e9eff4a"><span class="doxyHighlight">    <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/module/#a0a5c55e12c97b80021330fe82b642293a2486ec4ce4f33e42da3ad60d6e9eff4a">AppendUnique</a> = 6,</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00145" /><CodeLine lineNumber="145"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00146" /><CodeLine lineNumber="146"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">    /// Takes the max of the two values, which are required to be integers.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00147" /><CodeLine lineNumber="147" lineLink="/docs/api/classes/llvm/module/#a0a5c55e12c97b80021330fe82b642293a89821032d3b24b6a135f1d5acfbcd2c8"><span class="doxyHighlight">    <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/module/#a0a5c55e12c97b80021330fe82b642293a89821032d3b24b6a135f1d5acfbcd2c8">Max</a> = 7,</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00148" /><CodeLine lineNumber="148"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00149" /><CodeLine lineNumber="149"><span class="doxyHighlightComment">    /// Takes the min of the two values, which are required to be integers.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00150" /><CodeLine lineNumber="150" lineLink="/docs/api/classes/llvm/module/#a0a5c55e12c97b80021330fe82b642293a74e5a703504f88f6b34e9f31e8ae5160"><span class="doxyHighlight">    <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/module/#a0a5c55e12c97b80021330fe82b642293a74e5a703504f88f6b34e9f31e8ae5160">Min</a> = 8,</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00151" /><CodeLine lineNumber="151"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00152" /><CodeLine lineNumber="152"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Markers:</span></CodeLine>
